# Time Complexity

For Tree:

```text
O(N)
```

Every node visited once.

---

# Space Complexity

Queue stores one level.

```text
O(W)
```

Where:

```text
W = Maximum Width of Tree
```

Worst Case:

```text
O(N)
```

---

# DFS vs BFS Quick Comparison

| Feature | DFS | BFS |
|----------|------|------|
| Data Structure | Stack/Recursion | Queue |
| Traversal | Depth First | Level First |
| Memory | Less | More |
| Shortest Path | No | Yes |
| Level Order | No | Yes |
| Tree Height | Easy | Easy |
| Diameter | Easy | Not Preferred |

